platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Is your mind whirring away with all the things you need to do at work, home, and everywhere in between? Give your brain a break by logging your thoughts in Notion. Notion is a digital notepad in which you can jot down all sorts of information. Create private pages for lists, random thoughts and diary entries, or shared ones for documents youd like to invite friends and colleagues to so you can collaborate.
